甲醇(methanol)+哥士的(NaOH, KOH) 去水解CS，D CS會分解，但二噁英唔會。甲醇好易蒸發，你吸咗甲醇蒸氣，身體會將佢變成更加毒同嘅甲醛(methanal)，死快D。冇防毒衣同防化武豬咀，清潔唔到。"},{"pid":"9721acb5d83e5dcc0e47859f054a7255c8085aec","tid":1722463,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42d55cb46220f7690d3759dac7e937439171849e","tid":1722463,"uid":48083,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vi6efOV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvi6efOV.png&h=27e47fbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:17:01.000Z","msg":"完美"},{"pid":"9664457f78fff86176f8f591dba579efd5065b4b","tid":1722463,"uid":270281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:17:18.000Z","msg":"原來攻學校就係為咗整個大台俾大家, 多謝晒"}]}